Package: penCalc
Version: 0.1-1
Date: 2016-06-13
Type: Package
Title: A package to simulate the monthly pension received by a person
Authors@R: c(person("Renuka", "Sane", email = "renukas@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre")))
Author: Renuka Sane <renukas@gmail.com>, Arjun Gupta <arjung93@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Arjun Gupta <arjung93@gmail.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.5)
Imports: xtable,zoo,reshape,grid
Description: A package to simulate the expected monthly pension at retirement. The simulations require assumptions on wages, contribution rate, inflation, investment portfolio consisting of government bonds, corporate bonds, equities, expected returns on each asset class, and annuity prices.
